snippet.title: The Victor Initiative: Chapter 1 | Steam Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Play the first chapter here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3296220/The_Victor_Initiative__Chapter_1_Demo/
Wishlist the full game on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3285960/The_Victor_Initiative/

The Victor Initiative is a first-person horror game about delving into a government research centre and uncovering its secrets. What awaits you in there is anyone's guess...

To stay in the loop, join the official Spacepiano Games discord server here:   / discord  

I use Unity as my game engine.
